data.description: Presenting a stunning residence situated in the highly sought-after Sunburst Lakes community. This captivating home boasts an inviting open floor plan, seamlessly integrating the kitchen with a spacious dining area and an expansive family room. Throughout the entirety of the home, a tasteful luxury vinyl flooring graces the floors, enhancing its elegant appeal, with the exception of the laundry room. The main floor features a generously sized office space, versatile enough to function as a potential fourth bedroom, catering to a range of preferences and needs. Ascending to the upper level, the master bedroom impresses with its abundant spaceeasily accommodating king-size furnishings. The master bath area offers a sense of luxury with his and her sinks, complemented by a separate shower and an indulgent soaking tub. The additional bedrooms maintain a comfortable size, ensuring ample living space for all residents. Overlooking a serene pond and a private backyard, a spacious sunroom adds to the home's allure, providing a tranquil retreat for relaxation and contemplation.  Meticulously maintained, this property is offered in impeccable move-in condition, allowing you to seamlessly transition into your new abode. Notable updates include a new main roof installation in 2019, ensuring durability and peace of mind, and a recent replacement of the garage roof, completed within the last month. This home presents a unique opportunity to embrace refined living within a desirable community, making it a must-see for discerning buyers seeking both style and functionality.
